Title: 调用关系图
Describe: 关键跨模块调用链，覆盖普通图运行与 prebuilt agent/tool 路径。
------------------------------------------------------------
[Example]
S06_CALL_RELATIONSHIPS：用户图运行调用链

[Description]
普通用户路径可以概括为：用户代码调用 `StateGraph` builder，编译成 `CompiledStateGraph/Pregel`，运行时由 loop 和 runner 调度节点，checkpoint/store/cache/stream 作为横切能力接入。

[UML]
@startuml
participant "User Code" as User
participant "StateGraph" as Builder
participant "CompiledStateGraph/Pregel" as Pregel
participant "PregelLoop" as Loop
participant "PregelRunner" as Runner
participant "BaseCheckpointSaver" as Saver
participant "StreamMux/Transformers" as Stream

User -> Builder: add_node / add_edge / compile
Builder --> User: compiled graph
User -> Pregel: invoke or stream
Pregel -> Loop: enter run loop
Loop -> Saver: load latest checkpoint
Loop -> Runner: execute prepared tasks
Runner --> Loop: writes, interrupts, errors
Loop -> Saver: persist checkpoint and writes
Loop -> Stream: emit values, updates, messages
Pregel --> User: output or stream chunks
@enduml

[Detail]
这张序列图强调调用顺序。`BaseCheckpointSaver` 不是每次运行都必须存在，但当传入 checkpointer 时，它决定 `thread_id`、resume、time travel 和 interrupt 后恢复能力。`StreamMux/Transformers` 代表 `libs/langgraph/langgraph/stream/*`，它把内部运行事件转换为 `values`、`updates`、`messages` 等用户可见模式。
------------------------------------------------------------
[Example]
prebuilt ReAct agent 调用链

[Description]
`create_react_agent` 是 deprecated 但仍在 `prebuilt` 中的重要路径。它把 model、prompt、tools、state schema、checkpointer/store 和 interrupt 配置组装成一个 `StateGraph`。

[UML]
@startuml
participant "create_react_agent" as Factory
participant "Prompt Runnable" as Prompt
participant "Chat Model" as Model
participant "ToolNode" as ToolNode
participant "StateGraph" as Graph

Factory -> Prompt: build prompt runnable
Factory -> Model: bind_tools when needed
Factory -> ToolNode: wrap BaseTool/callables
Factory -> Graph: add agent node
Factory -> Graph: add tools node and conditional route
Graph --> Factory: CompiledStateGraph
loop while AIMessage has tool_calls
  Model -> ToolNode: tool_calls
  ToolNode --> Model: ToolMessage or Command
end
@enduml

[Detail]
`create_react_agent` 位于 `libs/prebuilt/langgraph/prebuilt/chat_agent_executor.py:278`。它校验 `version in ("v1", "v2")`、state schema 必含 `messages` 和 `remaining_steps`，必要时调用 `.bind_tools()`。`ToolNode` 负责工具并发执行、错误处理、state/store/runtime 注入和 `Command` 返回值。v2 模式通过 `Send` 将 tool call 分发给多个 tool node 实例，这是与 v1 的重要行为差异。

